 rchestra\, and associate conductor of the Pittsburgh Symphony. He is the 2
 022 recipient of The Sir Georg Solti Conducting Award. The Temerty Orchest
 ral Program at The Glenn Gould School\, the Royal Conservatory Orchestra i
 s widely regarded as an outstanding ensemble and one of the best training 
