BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:The Emperor - Beethoven\, Shostakovich\, Bach
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260502T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260502T193000
UID:2f28f647f58a670f4987c1cd3f2cfb7f@toronto.ca
DESCRIPTION:Wrapping up the 2025-26 season with works of eternal genius! T
 he superb young Toronto pianist Vanessa Yu joins the ensemble in one of th
 e greatest concertos of all time\, Beethoven's noble Piano Concerto No. 5\
 , the "Emperor". Music Director Nurhan Arman leads the orchestra in Dmitri
  Shostakovich's poignant and personal Chamber Symphony in C minor Op. 110a
  and finishes with the powerful reassurance of J.S. Bach's Contrapunctus 1
  and 2 in beautifully transparent orchestral versions.
LOCATION:George Weston Recital Hall\, Meridian Arts Centre\, 5040 Yonge St
 \, North York\, ON
URL:https://www.sinfoniatoronto.com/
X-SOURCE:City of Toronto Festivals & Events
