DESCRIPTION:Enjoy antiphonal performances of works for double choir by Eri
 c Whitacre\, Josef Rheinberger\, Urmas Sisask\, Swani Zubayeer\, Hussein J
 anmohamed\, and Caroline Shaw. We will deliver an unforgettable and immers
 ive choral-spatial experience! Come early for a pre-concert chat by Artist
 ic Director Thomas Burton.
