DESCRIPTION:A community-led arts and heavy music festival\, the first of i
 ts kind in the city! Founded by two lifelong friends\, Toronto-based conce
 rt promoter Denholm Whale and KW Campol of music management company Mythos
  and the Perpetual Flame Ministries record label/art house. Drawing inspir
 ation from European festival stalwarts like Roadburn\, Supersonic\, and Am
 plifest\, we're focused on heavy music as an ethos of collective catharsis
  more than a dedication to one specific metal subgenre. From burgeoning ar
 tists\, to favorites you never thought would reunite\, to one-off full alb
 um sets\, a heavily curated and meticulously planned lineup is the festiva
 l's key component.
