DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260606T200000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260606T200000
UID:aee7417132ec404b1d273b0035712cda@toronto.ca
DESCRIPTION:Amazing magic. Tremendous trickery. Hilarious antics. Get read
 y to have your mind blown! Watch as the world's most legendary magicians\,
  Pen and Teller celebrate their milestone anniversary. The celebrated duo 
 will blend classic favourites with astonishing new illusions\, all deliver
 ed with their trademark wit and showmanship for an unforgettable live expe
 rience. David Letterman lauds them as "evil geniuses—always amazing\, al
 ways entertaining\," while The New York Times hails their act as "a wither
 ingly funny\, brazen assault on the temple of magic\," and The Times of Lo
 ndon declares that "the comedy-magic duo are at their absolute peak:.
LOCATION:Meridian Hall\, 1 Front St E\, Toronto\, ON
URL:https://www.luminatofestival.com/PennTeller
X-SOURCE:City of Toronto Festivals & Events
END:VEVENT
